{"tid":2211633,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血換取的最大能量　禮志沖天的新氣象","createTime":"2020-09-21T08:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T09:04:38.000Z","uid":8968,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9da32159c99428de255cafc8da5efee401e051f0","tid":2211633,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"揮出一雙拳頭 大亨這妖獸 侵侵亦嚇走<br />\n驅趕奸黨泛民 才是個成就<br />\n<br />\n即使崎嶇難行 為爭取公允 泰博亦要忍<br />\n這小子 天生太勇敢 太幸運<br />\n全力盡力齋坐 要所有罪行立即停<br />\n全力用大亨本領 來為自由爭勝 Yeah Yeah Yeah<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=0373c47d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網<br />\n<br />\n熱血換取的最大能量 禮志沖天的新氣象<br />\n讓世上充斥正義能量 沒甚麼需要拯救和受傷<br />\n熱血便可得最大能量 立會沖天的新氣象<br />\n讓熱血充斥正義能量 以滿的英勇機智來獲取 這世上一切為我鼓掌<br />\n<br />\n就算滿多傷也未回望 奮勇的衝開POLY U<br />\n用正義的心向著前望 錦滿將這裡改變如獲選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22a815a00e40e1a15735742392fa64b193ec493","tid":2211633,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bdf0109c10d325859a5da2272d151f3d9047ad","tid":2211633,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a22a815a00e40e1a15735742392fa64b193ec493","tid":2211633,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T08:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB